<section id="slide-org2c15f77">
<h4 id="org2c15f77">The Guardian</h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/sep/05/detroit-riots-1967-lessons-uk%0A">Reading the Riot</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/news/datablog+technology/data-visualisation">Data Blog + Data Visualizations</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/data">Data</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/datablog/ng-interactive/2017/jun/27/census-stories-how-has-your-town-or-suburb-changed-over-10-years">Census Stories</a></li>
